{"tid":402234,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Microsoft玩到買薯片送X1X 每60秒送一部","createTime":"2017-09-16T09:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T13:37:55.000Z","uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"867ea644464dc39a5706eaf9b0cbd790764a8b55","tid":402234,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:22:52.000Z","msg":"　M$為了迎接&ldquo;最強遊戲主機&rdquo;Xbox One X上市，將展開大規模宣傳攻勢，其中包括土豪十足的促銷，著名飲品品牌&ldquo;Mountain Dew&rdquo;與著名薯片品牌&ldquo;Doritos&rdquo;聯合M$發布&ldquo;送機&rdquo;促銷，玩家買到的每瓶飲品與每包薯片都內含&ldquo;Key&rdquo;，這些Key將讓玩家有機會贏取主機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2017/09/20170916_cyl_36_17/gamersky_01origin_01_201791610408F8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2017%2F09%2F20170916_cyl_36_17%2Fgamersky_01origin_01_201791610408F8.jpg&h=f4b6652a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳細方法：<br />\n<br />\n　　收集&ldquo;Key&rdquo;，Xbox One X風格包裝的Mountain Dew與Doritos均有Key，包括新出的&ldquo;Mountain Dew Game Fuel Arctic Burst與Tropical Smash系列&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2017/09/20170916_cyl_36_17/gamersky_02origin_03_20179161040EC2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2017%2F09%2F20170916_cyl_36_17%2Fgamersky_02origin_03_20179161040EC2.jpg&h=08dfe9d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n銀行交易點券，從9月25日，玩家可以用這些Key轉換銀行交易點券，<a href=\"http://通過Every60Seconds.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8EEvery60Seconds.com&d=QRagY%2FDJ5g8sv7P2MEq5AdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=1e6f368d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">通過Every60Seconds.com</a>網站換取每日贏取遊戲機的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2017/08/20170819_cyl_36_26/gamersky_04origin_07_2017819957C2C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2017%2F08%2F20170819_cyl_36_26%2Fgamersky_04origin_07_2017819957C2C.jpg&h=43dcf410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDoritos與M$合作綠色薯片，搭配黑底包裝完美詮釋Xbox遊戲機<br />\n<br />\n　　下注贏取，從11月8日到12月15日，玩家可以用這些點券加入每日競拍，然後每日的下午9點到11點30的每60秒都將開獎送出一台Xbox One X遊戲機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2017/08/20170819_cyl_36_26/gamersky_02origin_03_201781995711A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2017%2F08%2F20170819_cyl_36_26%2Fgamersky_02origin_03_201781995711A.jpg&h=b0397beb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n包裝箱圖案設計致敬初代Xbox遊戲機<br />\n<br />\n　　Xbox One X搭載可以運行真正4K解像度的硬體設備，支持HDR與4K電影播放功能，普通版搭配1TB硬碟，售價499美元，預定11月7日發售，敬請期待。"},{"pid":"f88bc1e383ad07b820882664e61304e054449757","tid":402234,"uid":9284,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T09:27:22.000Z","msg":"賣唔出咪送"},{"pid":"a223d9552b5da522072c6b7325841fed366df695","tid":402234,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69da45ff14532aabecd5b487690b5cf54d0554a5","tid":402234,"uid":63303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T13:37:55.000Z","msg":"doritos係粟米片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}